rigade Combat Team|173rd ABN Brigade]]</center>\nFile:US Army 143rd ABN INF BN Flash.png|<center>173rd ABN Brigade's [[143rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|143rd Inf Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 1st BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd ABN Brigade's [[503rd Infantry Regiment (United States)|503rd Inf Regiment]], 1st Battalion</center>\nFile:US Army 2nd BN-503rd Inf Reg Flash.svg|<center>173rd ABN Brigade's 503rd Inf Regiment, 2nd Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Military Intelligence Corps (United States Army)|Military Intelligence]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:US Army SFC MI BN Flash.png|<center>[[1st Special Forces Command (Airborne)|1st Special Forces Command]]'s 389th Military Intelligence Battalion</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====[[Military Police Corps (United States)|Military Police]]====\n<gallery>\nFile:16 MP Bde flash.png|<center>[[16th Military Police Brigade (United States)|16th Military Police (MP) Brigade (BDE)]]</center>\nFile:US Army 21st MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 21st MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 65th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 65th MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 108th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 108th MP Company</center>\nFile:US Army 118th MP Co Flash.png|<center>16th MP BDE, 503rd MP Battalion's 118th MP Company</center>\n</gallery>\n\n====Multidisciplinary Commands====\n<gallery>\nFile:JSOC flash.png|<center>[[Joint Special Operations Command]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:USSOCOM flash.png|<center>[[United States Special Operations Command|Special Operations Command]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCAFRICA flash.png|<center>[[United States African Command|Special Operations Command Africa]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCCENT flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Central]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCEUR flash.png|<center>[[Special Operations Command Europe]]-Army Element</center>\nFile:SOCKOR flash.png|<center>[